	&lt;p data-end=&quot;213&quot; data-start=&quot;97&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;125&quot; data-start=&quot;97&quot;&gt;World Entrepreneurs&amp;#39; Day&lt;/strong&gt; is observed on &lt;strong data-end=&quot;154&quot; data-start=&quot;141&quot;&gt;August 21&lt;/strong&gt; every year to recognize the achievements of entrepreneurs.&lt;/p&gt;
