&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;United Nations (UN) Day 2025 celebrates the 80th anniversary of the UN Charter&amp;#39;s entry into force in 1945.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;The theme for the 80th anniversary is &amp;ldquo;Building our future together,&amp;rdquo; highlighting global collaboration for a sustainable and peaceful future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &amp;ldquo;Our Common Agenda&amp;rdquo; report guides the initiatives for the 80th anniversary, advocating stronger global governance.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The report emphasizes the urgent need for accelerating the implementation of Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UN Day 2025 serves as a call to action for global cooperation in addressing common challenges and building a sustainable future.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This year&amp;rsquo;s celebration marks the UN&amp;rsquo;s role in fostering peace, security, human rights, and development across the globe.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;United Nations (UN) Charter&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Officially entered into force on October 24, 1945, establishing the UN as an international organization focused on global peace and cooperation.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The UN Charter defines the organization&amp;rsquo;s goals, principles, and the structure of its various agencies and bodies.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Common Agenda Report&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;This report, published by the UN, sets out a comprehensive agenda for the future, stressing the need for global action on climate change, inequality, and social justice.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The report advocates for a revitalized global governance system, aiming to address emerging global challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The SDGs are a set of 17 global goals established by the United Nations in 2015 to address issues like poverty, health, education, gender equality, and climate action.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;These goals aim to promote prosperity while protecting the planet and ensuring peace and justice for all people.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
